put on the latest creations and...

108
00:09:41,594 --> 00:09:44,392
walk up and down
in front of the customers.

109
00:09:44,464 --> 00:09:47,194
Well, I guess you could be right.

110
00:09:47,267 --> 00:09:49,394
- Now, when these men...
- Men?

111
00:09:49,469 --> 00:09:52,734
