123
00:10:38,384 --> 00:10:42,013
Lily! Lily!

124
00:10:42,088 --> 00:10:44,318
You come right down here this minute!

125
00:10:44,390 --> 00:10:47,757
I am not gonna let her take that job,
and that's that!

126
00:10:47,827 --> 00:10:50,318
