[Laughing]

167
00:13:22,548 --> 00:13:27,315
You know, I've always felt
rather simpatico with Frankie.

168
00:13:27,386 --> 00:13:30,082
Okay, Herman, down the hatch.

169
00:13:35,094 --> 00:13:37,028
